data.description: 2-story pristine home boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths within a gated community. The open concept design on the lower level welcomes you with neutral colors, bathing the space in natural light. Ceramic tile and carpeting grace the floors, creating a harmonious blend of style and comfort. The kitchen is a chef's delight, marrying functionality with granite countertops and complementing with a generously sized kitchen island illuminated by recessed lighting. The owner's suite, located downstairs, features a ceiling fan and a well-appointed bathroom with a separate shower, garden tub, and double vanity.  Two secondary bedrooms on the lower level ensure ample living space, while an additional bedroom upstairs enjoys its own full bath. The upstairs game room with a closet, offers versatility for various lifestyles.  The garage has epoxy flooring and cabinetry. Stepping into the backyard, you'll find an entertainer's haven-a covered patio/deck extension and an outdoor kitchen beckon gatherings under the open sky. Sprinkler system front & back. It's been approved for construction of a middle school and will be located behind the elementary school. The elementary and upcoming middle school are within walking distance. The home is situated in close proximity to shopping and major highways.  Recent upgrades, including a roof and water heater replacement in 2023.
